                                    <watches>2</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13777228" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 07:32:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;String PropertyStates currently returns the length of the String as the size. This is not quite correct because each character requires two bytes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777240" author="mduerig" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 07:50:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The intention was to be in line with &lt;tt&gt;Property.getLength()&lt;/tt&gt;, which explicitly mandates this. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777242" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 07:53:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hmm, but it is in line with the JCR spec:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.day.com/specs/jcr/2.0/3_Repository_Model.html#3.6.7%20Length%20of%20a%20Value&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.day.com/specs/jcr/2.0/3_Repository_Model.html#3.6.7%20Length%20of%20a%20Value&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll just fix the estimate in KernelNodeState then.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777251" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 08:05:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in revision &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1526123&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1526123&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777361" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 11:13:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Need to reopen. The estimate is still not accurate enough.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777385" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 12:13:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adjusted the shallow size of String instances.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1526163&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1526163&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13790513" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Wed, 9 Oct 2013 15:29:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;bulk close for 0.10 release&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
